<section id="slide-orgfe7ef0d">
<h2 id="orgfe7ef0d">Expected Outcome</h2>
<ul>
<li class="fragment appear">Provide a simple introduction to using flashcards,  active recall &amp; spaced repititon for learning</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Eliminate the need to constantly read or make notes on the same topics</li>
<li class="fragment appear">Help make studying a daily habit</li>

</ul>
